        <h4>How long have you been doing this?</h4>
        <p>Jen conceived the Turtle Shelter Project in 2015 to help prevent people experiencing homelessness from freezing to death. We officially incorporated on April 3, 2017—Jen's sobriety anniversary—and received our 501(c)(3) status in 2018.</p>
        <p>We began in September 2017 with 450 volunteer hours, producing 50 prototype vests for testing. As of November 2024, we have distributed over 5,500 vests. With growing resources and improved efficiency, we recently produced and distributed 980 vests in under a month.</p>
